{"tid":1563797,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【逃犯條例】政府擬取消國慶煙花匯演 (19:15)","createTime":"2019-09-12T14:03:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T14:16:57.000Z","uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"62c63a623e6f16a43d62befc17531378d1e82c5c","tid":1563797,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:03:58.000Z","msg":"【逃犯條例】政府擬取消國慶煙花匯演 (19:15)<br />\n(明報)<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190912/s00001/738f2018d4e0b8665acc534e32139b0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190912%2Fs00001%2F738f2018d4e0b8665acc534e32139b0f.jpg&h=eec632d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1之1 - 去年的國慶煙花匯演。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n反修例運動持續，據了解，政府計劃取消10月1日晚的國慶煙花匯演。消息透露，政府憂慮當天會有大批人潮聚集，擔心造成衝突事件，近日商討是否適宜繼續放煙花，現時傾向取消較穩妥。港府在2013年曾因南丫海難及2014年佔領行動而取消國慶煙花匯演。<br />\n<br />\n今年國慶煙花，由全國政協常委許榮茂的世茂集團獨家贊助。有港府官員表示，按以往做法，如果要放煙花，近日便要公布各項安排，主辦方也會開記者會介紹煙花特色，但現時各方還未有信息如何處理，料政府稍後會有公布。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員林卓廷表示，目前社會氣氛不宜放煙花，因社會「很多傷痛未完」，放煙花與當下氣氛格格不入。他又稱，「10‧1」是敏感日子，相信屆時社會氣氛較緊張，有人聚集抗議放煙花風險亦不低。<br />\n<br />\n行會成員、新民黨主席葉劉淑儀亦稱，現時香港撕裂，放煙花期間不同政見市民或有人出言不遜，導致對罵、碰撞，故在目前環境，聚集多人看煙花會有危險。她又稱，今年是國慶70周年，特區政府亦有大觀禮團上京，「在北京慶祝最隆重」。"},{"pid":"08fb11ad7046c4331c3a47d91da7f26899ccc9d3","tid":1563797,"uid":55130,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:04:36.000Z","msg":"仆街 比完錢連煙花都唔放下"},{"pid":"2c2c1d8691ced9b26b63242b3a56d371a211bf68","tid":1563797,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:04:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"7e7acdc21c0f57bf87873079c99d50e67a10fa1d","tid":1563797,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:06:08.000Z","msg":"放煙花 有咩好怕喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c0fc780c7e9010114db55551315420649ed4cf","tid":1563797,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:06:48.000Z","msg":"南丫海難國殤日，應該永久取消煙花、煙火"},{"pid":"775796c4dd0a832a07c5d27ed3120cc8ff9174bd","tid":1563797,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:08:44.000Z","msg":"唔係咁能開心呀話"},{"pid":"cdf448e486a08afc39e757b8d79c9e443115e4a0","tid":1563797,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:10:08.000Z","msg":"唔放煙花咪放TG <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d620510b5f119a4c287b903ada24556b1bb8059e","tid":1563797,"uid":265179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:11:56.000Z","msg":"睇黎國慶個晚都係18區摧淚煙齊放<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414722bce4bb6a111ecf4b3186ac1f3fad9a8210","tid":1563797,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.g